I have been burned for Roleplaying, even on Firiona Vie, and I wish I could end it.  I'm rather disappointed at Verant for the way this server has come out -- in that there are so few events here, or at least big ones.  You'd think more quests would happen here, especially ones dealing with the storyline.<br>
<br>
